ross different LLM architectures and scales. We will conduct extensive ablation studies to ensure its generalizability.', '3. **Calibration of Precision Switching**: The precision-switching policy may require careful calibration to balance between latency and accuracy. We will use a combination of theoretical bounds and empirical validation to refine this policy.', '4. **Scalability to Larger Contexts**: While LASR is designed for efficient inference, its performance on ultra-long context tasks may be limited. We will investigate the scalability of the method to longer sequences and larger models.']}
