formation-theoretic approach may vary across different tasks and datasets. Additional experiments and fine-tuning may be required to ensure robust performance.', '4. **Theoretical Bounds**: The derived rate-distortion bounds may not always be tight, leading to suboptimal bit allocation in some cases. Further theoretical analysis and empirical validation are needed to refine these bounds.']}
